        "title": "Domain Model Catalog",
        "createdAt": "2026-04-03T15:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "The 21 concrete document models built on the Powerhouse platform \u2014 organized across Service & Pricing, Finance & Billing, Organization & Identity, Work Management, and Reporting zones",
        "orientation": "This MOC maps the concrete domain models that implement business logic on top of the Powerhouse document model framework. While the Document Model System MOC explains HOW models work (event sourcing, reducers, schemas), this MOC catalogs WHAT models exist and how they relate across 5 functional zones. The service-pricing chain (facet \u2192 template \u2192 offering \u2192 subscription \u2192 instance) is the most complex multi-model hierarchy."
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:49.000Z"
    }
